title: Amazing 1BR Grand Overlook- private entry- BEST FLOORPLAN EVER!
posting_body: ['The best floorplan ever!!', '-', 'I mean, if you like super charming and lots of natural light.', '🌞', 'You must see this SUPER fabulous one bedroom townhouse style apartment located in a gated community.', ' The 1BR Grand Overlook is the apartment of your dreams.', ' It features an open concept with large center island, spacious living space, a perfect sunroom area with curved archways and a French door that leads you to a very large private balcony.', 'This apartment home is full of natural light and charm-', 'it is a must see!', 'Call today to set up your own personal tour of this beauty in our AMAZING community.', 'https://youtu.be/bzlNMWhzEJ4', 'About Springs at Cobblestone Lake....', "You'll feel right at home the moment you step foot inside your Springs at Cobblestone Lake apartment offering studio, 1, 2 and 3 bedroom floor plans with a townhouse feel.", 'Your spacious luxury apartment includes design touches and quality finishes with optional private balconies or patios overlooking an inviting park-like setting, complete with resort style amenities.', 'High end details, including hardwood-style floors, walk-in closets, stainless steel appliances, in-home laundry and classic granite countertops combine pleasing form and practical function at every turn.', 'If home just isn’t home without your four-legged furry friend, then you’ll be happy to know that pets are welcome at Springs at Cobblestone Lake— no weight restrictions.', 'Special amenities have been designed specifically for them, including: on-site, leash-free pet playground, pet spa area for pampering your pooch and doggie DNA program to help keep the grounds clean and enjoyable for everyone.', ' 🐱🐶', 'Love ❤ where you live at Springs at Cobblestone Lake!', '💗 Love where you live 🏡 AND SAVE!!!']
